      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new workshop for some of our senior managers. Can you give me some general tips on grooming and appearance that help people look really authoritative and professional when they're in big boardroom meetings? Just like, what's the standard for looking high-level and polished?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
