      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Sure, I'd be happy to help. For a polished and authoritative appearance, it's best to maintain a neat and clean hairstyle, whether it's a classic cut or a more modern style. Dress in tailored, professional attire that fits well, avoiding clothes that are too tight or overly casual. Opt for neutral colors and high-quality fabrics, and always iron your clothes before dressing. Lastly, keep your shoes clean and polished, and consider a subtle fragrance to enhance your presence. These elements together can help you project a high-level, polished image in boardroom settings.",
